    Class Description
    org.cicirello.permutations.Permutation.Mechanic
    This class will be removed in the next major release, 4.0.0, and you should instead use the functionality provided by the Permutation.apply(PermutationUnaryOperator) and Permutation.apply(PermutationBinaryOperator,Permutation) methods, and the related PermutationUnaryOperator and PermutationBinaryOperator interfaces.
